## Using Commamnds
In the chat you'll have a commands serie to do certain actions to interact with the bot like **/start** command, so here we have the commands available:

- **/setup**:
    This command allow you set all the configuration about how the bot interacts with the integrations.
- **/update_board**:
    This command allow you update the trello board related by github issues.
- **/help**:
    This command allow you see an explanation how is this.
